[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      647[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     // Panel coherence rules encode known physiological relationships between
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      648[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     // results. They catch implausible combinations: lab errors, calibration
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      649[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     // drift across analytes, and specimen artifacts that manifest as impossible
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      650[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     // chemistry. These are rule-based, not ML, and they are among the most
